It is feasible to incorporate a field2d element containing a Pose2d member onto the dashboard. Here's how it was implemented:

```javascript
targetStationPoseField2d.setRobotPose(chassis.generateStationPose());
SmartDashboard.putData("SuperStructure/targetStationPose", targetStationPoseField2d);
```

You are encouraged to experiment with this approach.
